query_busy

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_busy -  This method tells us if the player/creator/lord is currently in busy mode.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mixed query_busy()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the busy mode flag

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/events.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method tells us if the player/creator/lord is currently in busy
mode.  This will be 1 if the creatopr is generaly busy, or
it will return the array of players they are busy with.
.EP

